This is the change log for Insulin4RL v1.0.1

=================
Insulin4RL v1.0.1
=================

Changes:
- Notebook updated to have distribution of time between states and distribution of delta_change doses
- Notebook updated to plot UMAP embedding after behavioural-cloning
